data.description: DEADLINE FOR OFFERS is Sunday, January 28, 2024 at 5:00 PM.   We will present offers as they come in and seller reserves the right to accept an offer at any time. Welcome to 8032 Saint Annes Court - a 3 level, 3 bedroom, 3 full-bath townhome in the welcoming community of Pinewood Lake. The light and bright eat-in kitchen kitchen is newly painted and has updated cabinets and a new dishwasher (2024). Main level living room and dining room have updated LVP flooring (2022), fresh paint and walkout to the deck. The upper level boasts 3 bedrooms including a primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom as well as another full bathroom. New carpet was installed in 2024 on the stairs, the hallway and in one of the bedrooms.  The other bedrooms have LVP flooring which was installed in 2022. The Lower level has new LVP flooring (2022), a nicely updated full bathroom and a bonus room that can be used as an office, a home gym or a reading nook. Pinewood Lake amenities include two designated parking spots in front of the house, walking paths around the lake, playground, community pool and community center. Fantastic location close to schools, parks, restaurants and shopping. Easy commuting with nearby bus stops and access to Rt 1, Rt 286, I-95 and I-495. Minutes to Kingstown (2.6 miles), Ft. Belvoir (3 miles), Wegmans.
